	measure 'Last Month - ACR' = ```
			
			VAR CurrMonth = MONTH ( TODAY() )
			VAR CurrYear  = YEAR ( TODAY() )
			
			VAR PrevMonth = IF ( CurrMonth = 1, 12, CurrMonth - 1 )
			VAR PrevYear  = IF ( PrevMonth = 12, CurrYear - 1, CurrYear )
			
			RETURN
			CALCULATE (
			    [Total ACR (USD)],
			 
			    'Calendar'[Month] = PrevMonth,
			    'Calendar'[Year]  = PrevYear
			)
			
			```
		formatString: \$#,0.###############;(\$#,0.###############);\$#,0.###############
		lineageTag: 933601cd-6d44-4db9-abd0-adcbb763dcbb

